<p><b>ST VINCENT DE PAUL THANKS YOU</b>. We visited a middle-aged woman who had 
her “dream job” at an upscale local restaurant. The manager gave her good 
performance evaluations and she was happy. Then the manager was replaced with a 
new manager who taunted her in a racist manner and soon she was forced to leave 
her dream job behind. She quickly found a new job but was without income while 
waiting to start work. With your financial support, we paid enough rent to keep 
her housed during this difficult time – thank you! <i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:bobclifford53@gmail.com?subject=St Vincent de Paul">Bob Clifford</a>, 
206-718-4158.</p>
